Nokia is ready to rock with amazing smartphones. This Year Nokia Comes in market to beat all brands. Nokia start our bussiness with mid-range smartphones : Nokia 6. It has full aluminum body with great features, its offer in the Price of $250 Dollars. Lets talk about the Advantages, Disadvantages , Features and Full Specification of Nokia . 
<h2> <b>Nokia 6 Advantages (Pros) </b></h2> 
<li> Yes It's VoLTE Confirmed From Nokia  </li>
<li> Nokia Offer Brillant Features Smartphone in <b>Mid-range Price</b>.</li>
<li> <b>5.5 inchs</b> Fully Aluminium body. </li>
<li> Protected with <b>Gorilla Glass 3</b> </li>
<li> Perfect for that user, who love to use too many Application and more other thing because it has <b>4GB of DDR3 RAM with (1.4GHz Octa-core (Qualcomm snapdragon 430) Processor).</b> </li> 
<li> <b> Aderno 505 GPU </b></li>
<li> All Sensors Available <b>( For GPS, Brightness, VR etc)</b></li>
<li> <b>16-megapixels</b> rear camera, f/2.0 with powerfull Dual-LED flash. </li> 
<li> <B>8-Megapixels</b>, f/2.0 front Camera </li>
<li> Runs on Latest <b>Operating System Android 7.0.1</b> with <b>Nokia Z launcher 13 With 2 Years Guarantee Updates
</b> (Its Provide very simple & Attractive user interface).</li>
<li> <b>Battery life is 3000 mAh</b>. Battery Backup is 10-11Hours with using Internet and battery backup on calling is 1.5Day.</li>
<li> <b>Fast Charging Support</b> (Full Battery Charge within 50-60minutes) </li>
<li> Faster Sense <b>FingerPrint Sensor</b> </li>
<li> <b>Dolby Sound Speakers</b></li> 
<h2> <strong>Nokia 6 Disadvantages (Problem & Issues)</strong> </h2>
<li> Non-Removable Battery</b>.</li>
<li> Hybrid Dual SIM SLOT : No you cant use simultaneously. either you can use one SIM and one Memory Card or Two SIM</li>
<LI> No backlight on capacitive keys</li>
<li> No Screen flash or No LED Flash on front camera </li>
<li> Some issue is reported for <b>Phone over heating</b> , we recommend user not to be over charge your phone, it's reduce your smartphone battery life.
